do_lagOut

public void do_lagOut(java.lang.String _name,
                      java.lang.String _message)
Called from a !lagout command, used to place a player back into a duel. To use this command: - must be playing in a duel - must be a spectator

Parameters:
_name - Name of the player requesting a lagout
_message - Anything else the player may have sent with the command
